= RSpec on Rails Changelog

== Version 0.3 (SVN)

* Renamed the Austar module to Spec
* Renamed Rake tasks and directorires: units->models, functional->controllers.
* Moved default fixture_path to spec_helper.rb and made it point to spec/fixtures.
* Imported code from http://lachie.info/svn/projects/rails_plugins/rspec_on_rails (Written by Lachie Cox)
* install.rb now creates RAILS_ROOT/spec/(unit+functional+fixtures) and copies PLUGIN_ROOT/files/spec_helper.rb (Chad Nantais <cnantais@gmail.com>)
* added rake task for running specs (spec, spec:functionals, spec:units) (Chad Nantais <cnantais@gmail.com>)

